title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sightseeing - Red Bull Ring
description:
In this video we will fly over the the F1 Circuit Red Bull Ring and try to follow the track using our Aviat Pitts Special S2S airplane.

After several passed you will hear the Bushtalk radio client kicking in and providing some nice explanation about the circuit.

If you also want to have some nice explanations about POI's which you are passing during your flight go the to site of Bushtalk radio and download their client:

https://bushtalkradio.com/
